    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/00bc2f520f4bbfa77e1d201e7d605f92.avif?t=1765491318\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>游戏仍在开发中，可能会发生变化。欢迎关注我们的Discord服务器，并将游戏加入愿望清单！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恶梦之夜</h2>Appearances是一款单人第一人称恐怖解谜游戏，你扮演的是小苏茜，在家族别墅里由保姆照顾。在深夜，你听到了奇怪的刺耳声音，似乎专门为了唤醒你而设计。你的第一反应是找到保姆，但对于一个想象力丰富的孩子来说，夜晚可能是可怕的。祖母为你制作的音乐盒是最好的安慰来源，但很快你会发现附近有超自然的东西潜伏，这个音乐盒的作用远不止播放音乐。揭开家族的过去，结束这些梦魇般的幻象，取决于你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/3142b3d062d6b9d6053833b2ce6d64f8.poster.avif?t=1765491318\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/3142b3d062d6b9d6053833b2ce6d64f8.webm?t=1765491318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >平行世界</h2>进化成一个现代化的家族别墅，穿越这个走廊和房间的迷宫。然而，跟随一个神秘的祝福，你可能会进入一个由困扰你的实体居住的平行世界。环境变化，新的路径将向你开放。抓住这些机会逃脱，并揭示额外的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/7de0bfae029c5e8c4f887fbc8f4d87cd.poster.avif?t=1765491318\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/7de0bfae029c5e8c4f887fbc8f4d87cd.webm?t=1765491318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >音乐盒</h2>你祖母的音乐盒，它的音乐是唯一可以唤醒你的方式。利用这个音乐盒找到在这个事件充满的夜晚跟随你的实体，并且不要被发现。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/e32ca84cd17be497b6907c97997b83da.poster.avif?t=1765491318\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/e32ca84cd17be497b6907c97997b83da.webm?t=1765491318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >隐藏的秘密</h2>通过解决谜题揭示家族的秘密，并揭示真相。然而，请记住，你只是一个孩子，无法理解追逐你的实体。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/b53d8092b680457030f6cceb287b0204.poster.avif?t=1765491318\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/b53d8092b680457030f6cceb287b0204.webm?t=1765491318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >心理恐怖</h2>这款游戏灵感来自电影和电子游戏恐怖片的杰作，也受到了逃脱游戏的启发！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/1734f808d29079c551dfbbb26ec5bcac.poster.avif?t=1765491318\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2356640/extras/1734f808d29079c551dfbbb26ec5bcac.webm?t=1765491318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
